devdoc.details: Interface of the KIP-13 standard, as defined in the [KIP-13](https://kips.klaytn.com/KIPs/kip-13). * Implementers can declare support of contract interfaces, which can then be queried by others. * For an implementation, see `KIP13`.

supportsInterface(bytes4).details: Returns true if this contract implements the interface defined by `interfaceId`. See the corresponding [KIP-13 section](https://kips.klaytn.com/KIPs/kip-13#how-interface-identifiers-are-defined) to learn more about how these ids are created.     * This function call must use less than 30 000 gas.
